they even shot the dog.

215
00:30:30,891 --> 00:30:33,184
This is just
a deal gone wrong, isn't it?

216
00:30:33,268 --> 00:30:37,522
Yup. Appears to have been
a glitch or two.

217
00:30:41,153 --> 00:30:45,113
