with a shotgun.

220
00:30:54,582 --> 00:30:56,959
How come the coyotes
ain't been at them?

221
00:30:57,001 --> 00:30:59,127
I don't know.

222
00:31:03,926 --> 00:31:06,844
Supposedly, a coyote
won't eat a Mexican.

223
00:31:06,929 --> 00:31:09,388
