than one fracas. Execution here.

225
00:31:13,852 --> 00:31:16,229
Wild West over there.

226
00:31:17,189 --> 00:31:21,651
- It's that Mexican brown dope.
- Oh, these boys is all swole up.

227
00:31:21,694 --> 00:31:24,570
